    "text": "The theory is a note taking/knowldge graph app (or any other kind of graph that is is just a tree + sparse edges) should better be edited as a graph, but current presentation of the graph makes navigation/editing awkward. that's why people are not creating these knowledge graphs (with typed edges/node schema)",
